        "duriFirsttext2": "<p>We believe nail care should be as healthy as it is beautiful. That’s why our products are vegan, cruelty-free, paraben-free, and long-lasting—crafted with clean ingredients in state-of-the-art U.S. facilities.</p><ul><li>vegan  & Cruelty-Free – ethically made</li><li>No Harsh Chemicals – paraben-free formulas.</li><li>Made in the USA – clean, quality ingredients</li></ul>",
