        "duriFirsttext2": "<p>Since 1990, Duri has been a family-owned brand dedicated to creating safe, effective nail and body care. What started with a passion for better formulas has grown into a collection of over 150 clean, cruelty-free products trusted by salons and individuals a like.</p><p>At the heart of our story is the award-winning Rejuvacote Nail Growth System, alongside a full range designed to strengthen, protect, and beautify naturally. Three generations later, we remain committed to blending family values with innovation — helping your natural beauty shine, one polish at a time.<br/></p>",
